data.description: Welcome to this VERY spacious and inviting 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom home! This move-in ready gem is nestled on a great level yard, offering plenty of room for your family to grow and thrive. Step inside to discover the allure of beautiful tigerwood floors that add warmth and elegance to the living spaces. And on chilly nights, two cozy fireplaces promise to keep you warm and snug. The open kitchen, with updated appliances, beckons you to whip up delightful meals for loved ones. The master ensuite offers a retreat, providing a perfect sanctuary after a long day. Venture upstairs, where you'll find even more options for relaxation and entertainment. A huge bonus room and a well-appointed media/theatre room invite hours of enjoyment and bonding with friends and family. Need a quiet space for work or study? The upstairs also features a versatile BR/Office area with nice built-ins to suit your needs. The best part? NO HOA. Plus, you're just a short and easy drive away from town, ensuring convenience and accessibility to all your daily needs. With many options, this home offers the perfect canvas for your dream lifestyle.
